nager(null);`.\n - How to use the latest SNAPSHOT version?\n   - Define OSS Sonatype repository in `~/.m2/settings.xml` as follows:\n     ```xml\n     <settings>\n         <servers>\n         ...\n         </servers>\n         <profiles>\n             <profile>\n                 <id>local</id>\n                 <activation\n\n-- getValue -1\n\n-- javassist -1\n\n-- add-opens -1\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782520354434}}
